<br>
Anyway, I was at the opening ceremonies of the tavern with my fiance, Joxer -- I'm sure you all know him -- and I had a great time. The cannonball contest was a lot of fun, even though I think I got sick.. ::chuckles, then coughs:: I'm glad to see the tribe thriving so. I'll work hard to gain more experience points. Again, the tavern's great!<br>
<br>
XAmazonGabrielle<br>
